item.title: CVE-2023-0144|2024-08-02T05:02:43.772Z -- unknown -- event%20manager%20and%20tickets%20selling%20plugin%20for%20woocommerce
item.description: The Event Manager and Tickets Selling Plugin for WooCommerce WordPress plugin before 3.8.0 does not validate and escape some of its post meta before outputting them back in a page/post, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
